Big facelift on legislator detail scraping.

- Separate downloading from parsing;
- Separate data_dir from source_data_dir;
- Fix photo url by stripping diacritics;
- Abide to new data_dir structure;
- Fetch details *and* bio pages;
- Simplify parsing;
- Output JSON instead of CSV (bio info needs a little more structure,
- like arrays for legislatures).

Right now we're not parsing everything we're fetching. Need to add the
rest.

